## Input

```css
.calls {
  one-positional-arg: one-positional-arg(a,);
  two-positional-args: two-positional-args(a,b,);
  one-keyword-arg: one-keyword-arg($a: z,);
  two-keyword-args: two-keyword-args($a: y,$b: z,);
  mixed-args: mixed-args(y, $b: z,);
}

.function-name {
  // TODO(interpolation support): start: #{1 + 1}foo(arg);
  // TODO(interpolation support): mid: foo#{1 + 1}bar(arg);
  // TODO(interpolation support): end: foo#{1 + 1}(arg);
  // TODO(interpolation support): full: #{foo}(arg);
  width: max($numbers...);
  width: max($numbers    ...);
  width: max($numbers/**/...);
  prop: fn(value    ...);
  prop: fn(value/**/...);
  color: rgba(50 50 0.50 50...);
}





